##We are from Hubei, now scattered around a family

Micro-signal Xinminzhoukan

Function description, depth and angle —— this is what we can do.

Looking down from an air plane, the five fingers of a family formed a fist of encouragement and encouragement as the palm of one's hand was held together unconsciously by the Wechat Group on this mobile phone screen

By Liu Fang

Looking down from an air plane, the five fingers of a family formed a fist of encouragement and encouragement as the palm of one's hand was held together unconsciously by the Wechat Group on this mobile phone screen

By Liu Fang

A mobile phone screen, can remit world affairs.

Our family wechat group, although not too large, but also almost cover a small half of China: sister is the first, guarding the hometown of Huangshi, Hubei; I ranked second, 30 years in Suzhou, Jiangsu; brother Third, home in southwest Chongqing Yongchuan; The fourth eldest sister, not far from home, listens to the bells of the Jianghan Pass in Hankou for a hundred years. The Fifth Sister, the furthest, travels south across Nanling Mountains to marry in Hong Kong.

Usually in the group, family affairs, state affairs, World Affairs, wind and rain sound reading sound, there should be all, topics rambling, what can be left text. Sometimes lazy do not want to pinch the words, do not want to roll up the tip of the tongue to speak mandarin, with a few dialect Voila. Whoever gets what reward must dry in the group. WHO has an open mind, also have to be released in the group, we have seven words 80 discussion, free to talk about ideas. Even burn a what good side dish, also want to send a picture to come up, let the small family group color, smell and taste complete.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The eldest sister and the fourth brother are stationed in Hankou

On the 29th day of the 12th month in the year of the pig, the last working day of the Lunar New Year, everything changed suddenly. The outbreak in Wuhan grew rapidly, and to control the spread of the disease, the brave men of Wuhan broke their wrists in The Parting of the Ways.

I speak. Because the simplest and most effective way to control the epidemic is to cut off the source of the spreading pollution in time. To the whole country and even the world a chess consciousness, the city is a ruthless Tibetan love.

Big sister immediately posted a two green tears long expression.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The roof of the four sisters'building overlooks the Tongji Hospital for new pneumonia patients. The Yellow House on the left is the Tongji Medical College student apartment, the Middle One is the Tongji hospital surgery building, and the right one is the Tongji hospital complex.

Little sister posted a song, Pearl of the Orient. The song sings: The River Bends to the east, flows to the Fragrant River to have a look, the Oriental Pearl my lover, whether your elegant demeanor is romantic still..

The one in my brother's hair is an emoticon with a sweaty forehead. "there is no lack of romance in Hong Kong, but the accommodation is too crowded. It is OK for mainlanders to go sightseeing, but they can not live in Hong Kong. It is certainly not realistic for the eldest sister and her two families to come to Hong Kong. I vote against it, " he said

I send a thumb map, praise: " 'Chongqing People' very rational, reasonable! "

My sister quickly sent me another poem, I use my broken palm, by Dai Wangshu. The poem was written during the Second Sino-japanese War, when the poet was imprisoned and tortured in Hong Kong during the Anti Japanese struggle for national salvation. After being released on bail, he felt his wounds, thought of the broken of his country, hated the invaders with his teeth, and felt his love for his country. I understand the meaning of this poem. Her "damaged palm" does not refer to the current epidemic situation, but compares the five of us to five fingers of different lengths, forming a palm. Now the palm hurt, pain is connected to the heart of the ten fingers.

I sent out a smiley face. In order not to let the atmosphere too depressed, I sent in the group of words some "over the hill beating the cow. ". I quote a poem by Li Bai: "The old West left the yellow crane tower, fireworks march to Yangzhou, " and said, after Yangzhou to set sail, it is Suzhou. My house in Suzhou is so big that it is no problem to receive my eldest sister and her two families. Hubei sent to Suzhou a Wu Zixu, he like heaven and earth, phase soil and water to build the 2,000-year-old city, this ancient city should be most grateful for Hubei. Now Hubei is in trouble, how can I help you, generous reception? Moreover, the ancient poem "the Maple Bridge Mooring at night" , which made Suzhou famous, was written by Zhang Ji, a native of Xiangyang, Hubei Province. If you don't believe me, listen to it on the ground.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
On the Tenth Day of the Lunar New Year, Liu Fang was at work

The idea of going to Suzhou is much more practical and realistic than that of going to Hong Kong, and Suzhou does have a deep relationship with Hubei, which is one of the feasible plans, he said. But the second brother in Suzhou is eating the news, very busy, to go is not only a accommodation problem, but also a series of life and work aspects of the package of projects to be solved, it seems to be hard. Why don't you launch a programme -- Harvard to Chongqing. In those days, the Japanese invaded China and occupied more than half of China in a moment of arrogance, but Chongqing was a hard nut they could not crack. Wuhan is a hero city, Chongqing is not a hero city? Afraid of its little virus? To come to Chongqing, my house is bigger than Suzhou's, and I am not a migrant worker. I have my own economic entity to take care of. If big sister and big sister do not mind, they can help me to run my business in Chongqing, and my work and life are all properly settled, it's the best way to attack, retreat, and defend.

She said she could drive to Hankou to pick up her sister's family even if the city was closed. She is familiar with Wuhan's route, bypassing high-speed exits and taking more provincial and less important routes, which can easily break through the encirclement.

Big sister has a driver's license, driving skills outstanding, bring out a lot of disciples, many of whom are much older than her. Usually New Year, give her New Year's apprentice happened to be able to make up two tables. She really knows her way around Wuhan.

Big sister smiled, gave big sister a thumb, said: it can be called seven in seven out of Battle of Changban's lone hero female version of Zhao Zilong! However, more than 10 million people in Wuhan, how do you save? Is there room for so many people out there if we all want to escape?

Big sister know big sister said is ironic, temporarily speechless, can only respond to a red face sweating expression.

The elder sister went on to say, there is a saying: No snowflake is innocent in an avalanche. There are many interpretations of this phrase, and many exceptions to it, but it is an apt one in the face of a possible outbreak. Then the snow white flawless, if joined the ranks of avalanches, then the snow changed color in an instant, into black or red. Eldest sister most understand the principle of gasoline, a person on fire, outside the house is the gasoline depot, can take the fire to run outside the house? No. The best way is to get down on the ground and put out the fire quickly. Otherwise, flight will not only result in the perpetrators of the outbreak, but will not be able to escape at all.

The big sister flashed a smiling face again, "panic is the common denominator of all stupidity and imbecility, " he said. And I'm going to give you a quote that makes it sound like we're on the same page. Ci Yue: Under the mountain banner is in sight, the mountain drum angle smells. I stood firm against the enemy's siege. Already fortified, even more united. "reports of a virus outbreak are coming in from the Yellow Sea. "

I like it. Yes! Yes! Yes! The word will be "enemy" to "virus" , accurate and vivid, and this was originally a battle without gunpowder smoke. Every man is a soldier, and none can be a spectator. If I understand correctly, the family back home is not ready to break out?

Big Sister said, the tree stands tall, why do birds and beasts scattered? Sworn to live and die with the Great Wuhan!

Little sister said, ok, ok, we from Hong Kong, Suzhou, Chongqing, together with the people of the whole country, to the family airdrop supplies home, in addition to masks and other health supplies, we will also express delivery of fresh vegetables.

Four younger sister home balcony to see the community
